00:00:38.370 --> 00:00:41.580
¿Te convertirás en mi amigo?

00:00:41.580 --> 00:00:43.770
Su alteza.

00:00:43.770 --> 00:00:45.470
Yo...

00:00:46.620 --> 00:00:50.560
